_sText: FY SUMMERPOOL BY UNREAL I got a sudden inspiration to make a map related to summer, so I remembered the old fy_poolday map that I used to play so much before I was even mapper. So I came up with this, a totally new version of fy_poolday, it has much more detail, and a nice ambient. Features: > nice environment > fishes > custom textures/models > drops > buyzone > bombsite (inside the pool) > 2 secondary roots I tried to keep everything like the original one, just changing the style, so thats the final result. Special thanks to TopHATTwaffle for providing really unique custom textures, and to whoever created the original version, I'm sorry, there are so many versions I simply don't know who is the real author. I hope you like it, Have fun.
